WEBVTT

00:03.571 --> 00:07.541
Excuse me.
Um... what's going on?

00:07.541 --> 00:10.378
The landlord smelled something
coming out of 6-B.

00:10.378 --> 00:13.114
He went in and found a body.

00:23.557 --> 00:27.195
Hi. Um, I'm friends
with the woman in 6-B.

00:27.195 --> 00:30.198
Can I--
Can I please come in?

00:30.198 --> 00:31.732
Yeah, sure.

00:31.732 --> 00:33.033
- Come on.
- Thank you.

00:38.639 --> 00:39.907
He says he knows her.

00:41.409 --> 00:44.778
- What's your name?
- Adam Carpenter.

00:44.778 --> 00:46.580
What's the nature
of your relationship

00:46.580 --> 00:48.015
to the deceased?

00:48.015 --> 00:50.218
I'm the father of her child.

00:50.218 --> 00:52.786
I'm sorry.

00:52.786 --> 00:54.855
What happened?

00:54.855 --> 00:56.023
No sign of forced entry.

00:56.023 --> 00:57.858
Looks like natural causes.

00:57.858 --> 00:59.693
Can't be sure till
the coroner weighs in.

00:59.693 --> 01:02.263
Did she have any known
medical issues?

01:02.263 --> 01:06.534
Uh, her prenatal doc said
she had a low

01:06.534 --> 01:08.035
red blood cell count,
but that it wasn't

01:08.035 --> 01:10.238
anything to be worried about.

01:10.238 --> 01:12.873
Give me a call in the morning.

01:12.873 --> 01:14.642
We'll take your full statement.

01:20.281 --> 01:23.584
Can I have a...
a minute in here?

01:23.584 --> 01:25.253
Take your time.

02:15.203 --> 02:17.371
<i>The lab received a strange call</i>

02:17.371 --> 02:19.540
<i>from the Fire Island
Park Service this morning.</i>

02:19.540 --> 02:21.975
<i>The rangers can't explain
how the deer</i>

02:21.975 --> 02:24.278
<i>are repopulating
so quickly there</i>

02:24.278 --> 02:26.547
<i>despite the culling
earlier this summer.</i>

02:26.547 --> 02:28.682
<i>I confess I can't
explain it either.</i>

