till after the show.

12:30.317 --> 12:32.252
Uh, I'm-I'm not here
for an autograph.

12:32.252 --> 12:35.588
Um, it's a matter
of public health.

12:35.588 --> 12:37.457
Really?

12:37.457 --> 12:40.427
Well, it's very kind of you
to finally show up.

12:40.427 --> 12:41.761
Sorry?

12:41.761 --> 12:44.564
I've been calling
you guys for weeks.

12:44.564 --> 12:48.235
