the Whore of Babylon.

13:15.295 --> 13:18.198
There's something new
going around.

13:18.198 --> 13:21.501
Something deadly.

13:21.501 --> 13:23.336
I'm just trying to keep
as many people safe as I can.

13:26.339 --> 13:28.375
It's my last show tonight.

13:28.375 --> 13:31.578
And it doesn't feel safe
around here anymore.

13:34.547 --> 13:37.184
- Last show?
- Mm-hmm.

13:37.184 --> 13:39.219
End of an era.

13:42.522 --> 13:45.058
I should have hung
my tiara up years ago.

13:45.058 --> 13:47.895
But I'm stubborn.

13:47.895 --> 13:49.997
Holding on to an old dream.

13:49.997 --> 13:53.066
But what a dream it was.

13:53.066 --> 13:57.704
All that music, all that love.

13:57.704 --> 13:59.806
Freedom incarnate.

13:59.806 --> 14:02.342
Vitality without shame.

14:02.342 --> 14:06.413
But it's gone now.

14:06.413 --> 14:09.182
I've sensed it coming
for a long time.

14:11.218 --> 14:12.585
It's over.

14:19.626 --> 14:21.361
Deadly, huh?

14:25.432 --> 14:29.502
Well, go with God,

14:29.502 --> 14:32.672
